statement: with duty_his as( select employee_id from ads_biz.ads_biz_employee_duty_his_cm t1 where t1.dmonth between '2023-01-01' and '2023-01-01' and t1.duty_id in (540,1527,541,537,1601,2058,1812,1316,897) and t1.duty_classify=10 and t1.sales_action_filter_flag = 1 group by employee_id) , v_auth as ( select auth_emp.employee_id as employeeId , employee_name as employeeName , duty_name as dutyName , responsible_department_name as responsibleDepartmentName , induction_duration as inductionDuration , arrival_duration as arrivalDuration , case when in_office = 10 then 1 else 0 end as isInOffice from ads_biz.ads_biz_emp_dept_relationship_td auth_emp join duty_his t1 on auth_emp.employee_id=t1.employee_id where 1=1 and ( auth_emp.lv5_id = 18667 or auth_emp.lv3_id = 15182 or auth_emp.lv3_id = 84) and auth_emp.lv3_id = 84 ) , v_waybill_double as ( select waybill_id , count() , 1 as is_double from dwd_pub.v_dwd_pub_seller_workorder_2h t1 where 1 = 1 group by waybill_id having count() > 1 ) , v_salesAmt as ( select create_employee_id ,sum(sales_amt) as totalSaleAmt ,sum(sales_amt_pre) as preTotalSaleAmt from ( select t1.create_employee_id , t1.waybill_id , max(if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31',t1.sales_amt,null)) as sales_amt , max(if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31',t1.sales_amt,null)) as sales_amt_pre from dwd_pub.v_dwd_pub_seller_workorder_2h t1 where 1=1 and dmonth >= '2022-12-01' and dmonth <= '2023-01-01' and create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' group by t1.create_employee_id,t1.waybill_id )t group by create_employee_id ) , v_workorder as ( select t1.create_employee_id , max(case when create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t2.is_double = 1 then 1 else 0 end) as is_reModify , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.type = 1,t1.workorder_id,null)) as workorderCnt , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.type = 2,t1.workorder_id,null)) as oaCnt , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31',t1.workorder_id,null)) as modifyCnt , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31',t1.waybill_id,null)) as votes , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31',t1.payment_customer_id,null)) as workorderCustCnt , sum(if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31',t1.sub_amount,null)) as workorderSubAmount , count(distinct case when create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t2.is_double = 1 then t1.waybill_id end) as reModifyVotes , count(distinct case when create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0 and t1.sign_profit*100/sign_amt < 0 then t1.waybill_id end) as loseMoneyReduceVotes , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0,t1.workorder_id,null)) as reduceCnt , sum(if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0,sub_amount,0)) as reduceSubAmount , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0,t1.waybill_id,null)) as reduceVotes , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0,t1.payment_customer_id,null)) as reduceCustCnt , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.sub_amount > 0,t1.workorder_id,null)) as raiseCnt , sum(if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.sub_amount > 0,sub_amount,0)) as raiseSubAmount , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.sub_amount > 0,t1.waybill_id,null)) as raiseVotes , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2023-01-01' and create_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.sub_amount > 0,t1.payment_customer_id,null)) as raiseCustCnt , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.type = 1,t1.workorder_id,null)) as preWorkorderCnt , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.type = 2,t1.workorder_id,null)) as preOaCnt , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31',t1.workorder_id,null)) as preModifyCnt , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31',t1.waybill_id,null)) as preVotes , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31',t1.payment_customer_id,null)) as preWorkorderCustCnt , sum(if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31',t1.sub_amount,null)) as preWorkorderSubAmount , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0,t1.workorder_id,null)) as preReduceCnt , sum(if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0,sub_amount,0)) as preReduceSubAmount , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0,t1.waybill_id,null)) as preReduceVotes , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0,t1.payment_customer_id,null)) as preReduceCustCnt , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.sub_amount > 0,t1.workorder_id,null)) as preRaiseCnt , sum(if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.sub_amount > 0,sub_amount,0)) as preRaiseSubAmount , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.sub_amount > 0,t1.waybill_id,null)) as preRaiseVotes , count(distinct if(create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.sub_amount > 0,t1.payment_customer_id,null)) as preRaiseCustCnt , count(distinct case when create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t2.is_double = 1 then t1.waybill_id end) as reModifyVotesPre , count(distinct case when create_date >= '2022-12-01' and create_date <= '2022-12-31' and t1.sub_amount < 0 and t1.sign_profit*100/sign_amt < 0 then t1.waybill_id end) as loseMoneyReduceVotesPre from dwd_pub.v_dwd_pub_seller_workorder_2h t1 left join v_waybill_double t2 on t1.waybill_id = t2.waybill_id where 1=1 and dmonth >= '2022-12-01' and injuryVacationDays , sum(maternity_vacation_times) as maternityVacationDays , sum(sick_hours) as sickDays , sum(personal_affairs_hours) as personalAffairsDays from ads_biz.ads_biz_seller_attendance_td t1 where t1.attendance_date >= '2023-01-01' and t1.attendance_date <= '2023-01-31' and t1.dmonth between '2023-01-01' and '2023-01-01' group by t1.employee_id ) , v_list as ( select * from ( select t4.injuryVacationDays , t4.maternityVacationDays , t4.sickDays , t4.personalAffairsDays , case when t1.is_reModify = 1 or (coalesce(t1.workorderSubAmount , 0)-coalesce(t3.totalSaleAmt , 0))>=0 then 1 coalesce(t1.workorderSubAmount , 0) as workorderSubAmount , coalesce(t1.workorderCustCnt , 0) as workorderCustCnt , coalesce(t1.reduceCnt , 0) as reduceCnt , coalesce(t1.reduceSubAmount , 0) as reduceSubAmount , coalesce(t1.reduceVotes , 0) as reduceVotes , coalesce(t1.reduceCustCnt , 0) as reduceCustCnt , coalesce(t1.raiseCnt , 0) as raiseCnt , coalesce(t1.raiseSubAmount , 0) as raiseSubAmount , coalesce(t1.raiseVotes , 0) as raiseVotes , coalesce(t1.raiseCustCnt , 0) as raiseCustCnt , coalesce(t3.totalSaleAmt , 0) as totalSaleAmt , coalesce(t1.reModifyVotes , 0) as reModifyVotes , coalesce(t1.loseMoneyReduceVotes , 0) as loseMoneyReduceVotes , coalesce(t1.workorderCnt , 0) - coalesce(t1.preWorkorderCnt , 0) as workorderCntDiff , coalesce(t1.oaCnt , 0) - coalesce(t1.preOaCnt , 0) as oaCntDiff , coalesce(t1.votes , 0) - coalesce(t1.preVotes , 0) as votesDiff , coalesce(t1.modifyCnt , 0) - coalesce(t1.preModifyCnt , 0) as modifyCntDiff , coalesce(t1.workorderCustCnt , 0) - coalesce(t1.preWorkorderCustCnt , 0) as workorderCustCntDiff , coalesce(t1.workorderSubAmount , 0) - coalesce(t1.preWorkorderSubAmount , 0) as workorderSubAmountDiff , coalesce(t1.reduceCnt , 0) - coalesce(t1.preReduceCnt , 0) as reduceCntDiff , coalesce(t1.reduceSubAmount , 0) - coalesce(t1.preReduceSubAmount , 0) as reduceSubAmountDiff , coalesce(t1.reduceVotes , 0) - coalesce(t1.preReduceVotes , 0) as reduceVotesDiff , coalesce(t1.reduceCustCnt , 0) - coalesce(t1.preReduceCustCnt , 0) as reduceCustCntDiff , coalesce(t1.raiseCnt , 0) - coalesce(t1.preRaiseCnt , 0) as raiseCntDiff , coalesce(t1.raiseSubAmount , 0) - coalesce(t1.preRaiseSubAmount , 0) as raiseSubAmountDiff , coalesce(t1.raiseVotes , 0) - coalesce(t1.preRaiseVotes , 0) as raiseVotesDiff , coalesce(t1.raiseCustCnt , 0) - coalesce(t1.preRaiseCustCnt , 0) as raiseCustCntDiff , coalesce(t3.totalSaleAmt , 0) - coalesce(t3.preTotalSaleAmt , 0) as totalSaleAmtDiff , coalesce(t1.reModifyVotes , 0) - coalesce(t1.reModifyVotesPre , 0) as reModifyVotesDiff , coalesce(t1.loseMoneyReduceVotes,0) - coalesce(t1.loseMoneyReduceVotesPre, 0) as loseMoneyReduceVotesDiff from v_workorder t1 join v_auth t2 on t1.create_employee_id = t2.employeeId left join v_salesAmt t3 on t1.create_employee_id = t3.create_employee_id left join v_attendance t4 on t1.create_employee_id = t4.employee_id where modifyCnt >0 )t where ( 1=1 ) ) select * from v_list where 1=1 and isToBeFocus = 1 order by responsibleDepartmentName DESC nulls last, employeeId limit 0, 5
